subject: Hi everyone !
author: neli_nelis
full_text:
Hello

I'm a newbie at this place and would like to know the meaning of some 
of my EVPs, as I have many of them, one of the last ones says: "COME 
WITH US, RECALL" then I asked who were they, and they told me "Ummitta 
people", I have seen ufos, but I don't know if they can give messages 
as the ones of EVP, the very last one, says: CAN YOU HEAR ME ? Wow ! I 
want to know who is trying to communicate with me, as the voice is so 
human that it doesn't seems to be a spirit, although they speak with 
low voice. But I am very astonished with the one of "come with us" 
and "Recall" I don't know what do I have to recall, I do my EVPs with 
my cell phone, I have time with this practice but lately the 
communications are so clear that I doubt that they can be of the spirit 
world, can some of you help me to understand the message please ???

Kind regards
Neli
